column1: Testing the Permissions provided by the module
View repository objects
column2: Toggle a user's permission to view repository objects, and navigate to an Oral History object
column3: User with permission to view repository objects can view OH objects. Users without this permission cannot view OH objects.

column1: Add datastreams to repository objects
column2: Toggle a user's permission to add datastreams to repository objects, and navigate to an Oral History Object, an attempt to add a datastream.
column3: User with permissions to add datastreams to repository objects can do so on OH objects. Users without this permission cannot add datastreams to OH objects.

column1: Edit metadata
column2: Toggle a user's permission to edit metadata and navigate to an Oral History Object. Attempt to edit metadata.
column3: User with permissions to edit metadata can edit metadata on OH objects. Users without this permission cannot add datastreams to OH objects.

column1: Create new repository objects
column2: Toggle a user's permission to create new repository objects and attempt to add an OH object.
column3: User with permissions to create new repository objects can ingest OH objects. Users without this permission cannot.

column1: Permanently remove objects from the repository
column2: Toggle a user's permission to permanently remove objects from the repository and attempt to remove them.
column3: User with permission to permanently remove objects from the repository can do so. User without this permission cannot.

column1: Manage object properties
column2: Toggle a user's permission to manage object properties.
column3: Users with the permission to manage object properties can manage object properties. Users without the permission to manage object properties cannot.

column1: View datastream history
column2: Toggle a user's permission to view datastream history.
column3: Users with the permission to view datastream history can do so. Users without the permission to view datastream history cannot.

column1: Revert datastream history
column2: Toggle a user's permission to revert datastream history.
column3: Users with the permission to revert datastream history can do so. Users without this permission cannot.

column1: Manage deleted objects
column2: Toggle a user's permission to manage deleted objects.
column3: Users with the permission to manage deleted objects can do so. Users without this permission cannot.

column1: Regenerate derivatives
column2: Toggle a user's permission to regenerate derivitives.
column3: Users with the permission to regenerate derivitives can do so. Users without this permission cannot.

column1: Replace datastreams
column2: Toggle a user's permission to replace datastreams.
column3: Users with the permission to replace datastreams can do so. Users without this permission cannot.

column1: Configuration Testing
Enable: Create WEBVTT file for captions or subtitles on an audio/video file.
column2: Enable "Create WEBVTT file for captions or subtitles on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories and ingest a file
column3: WEBVTT MEDIATRACK is created and can be found under Oral History Object > Manage > Datastreams

column1: Enable: Enable captions/subtitles display on an audio/video file.
column2: Enable "Enable captions/subtitles display on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: CC Caption button in player appears, along with captioning test if it is enabled

column1: Enable: Enable transcript display on an audio/video file.
column2: Enable "Enable transcript display on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: Transcript viewer appears below the oral history object, with Transcript tab, playback buttons, timecoded buttons for each cue

column1: Enable: Display media and transcript side-by-side on an audio/video file.
column2: Enable "Display media and transcript side-by-side on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: If transcript display is enabled: Oral history object and Transcript viewer are placed and scaled to fit horizontally, side by side. If transcript display is disabled: Oral history object is scaled to fit horizontally, transcript display is not viewable.

column1: Enable: Generate datastream for WebVTT indexing on an audio/video file.
column2: Enable "Generate datastream for WebVTT indexing on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories and ingest a file with a webvtt transcript
column3: XML INDEXMEDIATRACK is created and can be found under Oral History Object > Manage > Datastreams

column1: Disable: Create WEBVTT file for captions or subtitles on an audio/video file.
column2: Disable "Create WEBVTT file for captions or subtitles on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories and ingest a file
column3: With this option disabled, the MEDIATRACK datastream is not generated.

column1: Disable: Enable captions/subtitles display on an audio/video file.
column2: Disable "Enable captions/subtitles display on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: CC caption button in player and captions are not viewable

column1: Disable: Enable transcript display on an audio/video file.
column2: Disable "Enable transcript display on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: Transcript viewer is not visible when viewing oral history object

column1: Disable: Display media and transcript side-by-side on an audio/video file.
column2: Disable "Display media and transcript side-by-side on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: If transcript display is enabled: transcript viewer is visible below oral history object. If transcript display is disabled: oral history object is viewable, transcript viewer is not viewable.

column1: Disable: Generate datastream for WebVTT indexing on an audio/video file.
column2: Disable "Generate datastream for WebVTT indexing on an audio file" in admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories
column3: INDEXMEDIATRACK datastream is not generated

column1: Specify VTT default language code(s) on an audio/video file.
column2: In admin/islandora/solution_pack_config/oralhistories, Add and remove languages indicated in VTT file
